In honor of your departed loved one, we present our heartfelt Bald Eagle Funeral Prayer Card, adorned with a striking photo of a majestic bald eagle perched gracefully on a branch, with towering mountains in the background. This powerful image evokes a sense of strength, freedom, and natural beauty, offering solace and comfort during times of mourning.

Embrace Divine Comfort: Amidst the serene presence of the bald eagle, find solace in the comforting embrace of divine grace. Our prayer card serves as a beacon of hope, guiding grieving hearts towards inner peace and serenity as they navigate the journey of loss.

Personalized Tribute: On the back of the card, there’s a space for your loved one’s name and dates, serving as a heartfelt tribute to their memory. Below, there’s ample room for funeral poems, verses, or prayers, allowing you to customize the card with words of remembrance and reflection.

Eternal Remembrance: As the bald eagle rests majestically on the card, may it symbolize the enduring legacy and strength of your departed loved one’s spirit. May their memory be a source of comfort and inspiration, guiding you through moments of remembrance and reflection.

Guiding Light: Just as the bald eagle soars high above the mountains, may it serve as a guiding light during your journey of grief. The presence of the eagle honors the memory of your loved one and represents their enduring spirit and resilience.

Heartfelt Tribute: Honor the legacy of your loved one with heartfelt funeral poems, verses, or prayers on the back of the card. This personalized tribute is a meaningful way to express your love and gratitude for the impact they had on your life.

Everlasting Love: As you hold this prayer card in your hands, may it serve as a reminder of the enduring love and cherished memories you shared with your departed loved one. May it bring you comfort and peace, knowing that their spirit lives on in the hearts of those who loved them.

Embrace the majestic beauty of the Bald Eagle Funeral Prayer Card: a tribute to the enduring legacy of love and remembrance that transcends time and space. Price:$34.95
